          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 60,
              "body": "Since energy-saving-modes have been used in two different place, one is set as rw, the other place is set as ro, I am wondering whether we can define one grouping, reuses in two places, it looks hard. I am a little bit struggling about this.\r\nAlternatively we don't define grouping, Just define energy saving modes container  in two places, but it seems clumsy. ",
